{"tid":1360512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"哇屌 借力打力呀喂 文宣呀","createTime":"2019-07-24T11:09:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T15:34:26.000Z","uid":14087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0fb8562fe17118c2b77b2b68a65130b67b8ee25d","tid":1360512,"uid":14087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:09:10.000Z","msg":"無人理 <br />\n有冇得整張<br />\n<br />\n只要接納五大訴求(當然要重申邊五大)<br />\n立即可以修補社會撕裂<br />\n但林鄭為求面子 不接納社會聲音<br />\n林鄭殺港<br />\n想解放軍屠城<br />\n搞死香港<br />\n<br />\n有冇文學巴打可以改良下<br />\n<br />\n會員:驚察叔叔提供<br />\n<br />\n請大家一定要記得！！！！<br />\n１。全面撤回逃犯條例<br />\n２。撤銷暴動定性<br />\n３。釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n４。全面實行雙普選<br />\n５。成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任＋徹查警黑勾結元朗站暴打站內市民<br />\n6 。721上環對示威者開36槍 義士被狗開槍擊中 下落不明<br />\n要求公佈義士下落<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eb04fd9a2af9cbff3e1f1f923976a7c865f2e16","tid":1360512,"uid":14087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:27:03.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"db28a64275145bcf2b9a57447cd26de7e1d75980","tid":1360512,"uid":279085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:27:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzfNKZRPQHZk&d=ye2s6s2DGg0XurdvegCh9cFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=610e90a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk</a>"},{"pid":"d802b5acc9f23f8c011d163e1e23e72aae4815b2","tid":1360512,"uid":14087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:40:13.000Z","msg":"Hi"},{"pid":"e570a465d99fe1d546df52bcc3ae7ee57ab81853","tid":1360512,"uid":14087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:05:42.000Z","msg":"